PROGRAM:
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        System.out.print("Enter original string: ");
        String original = sc.nextLine();

        System.out.print("Enter character or word to replace: ");
        String target = sc.nextLine();

        System.out.print("Enter new character or word: ");
        String replacement = sc.nextLine();

        String updated = original.replace(target, replacement);

        System.out.println("\nOriginal string: " + original);
        System.out.println("Updated string : " + updated);
    }
}

OUTPUT:
Enter original string: meenu is my best friend
Enter character or word to replace: best
Enter new character or word: close

Original string: meenu is my best friend
Updated string : meenu is my close friend
